    "49 for a review).",
    "CAVE was particularly influenced by CATMAID 32, which enables collaborative annotation, manual neuron tracing and analysis, and was used by the Drosophila larva community 50 and initial manual reconstruction of the full adult fly brain dataset 38.",
    "Similarly, webknossos 34, Viking 35 and Knossos 33 (https://knossos.app) support collaborative manual tracing and annotating.",
    "For distributed proofreading, Eyewire 30 is the closest precedent, as it distributed block-based proofreading to a community through an interactive browser interface with remeshing capabilities after edits.",
    "NeuTu 26 demonstrated neuron-based proofreading at scale for a restricted group of people that proofread multiple Drosophila datasets, including the hemibrain 12."
